700305f-a.title: Bronx: 190th Street (West) - University Avenue
700305f-a.text:
West 190th Street (right), north side, east from University Ave.
to Aqueduct Ave. West, showing, prior to completion, two 6-story apart-
ment houses. The 2-unit building at the N.E. corner of University Ave.
is called the Willdan Court.
About 1929.
Enickerbocker Photo Service.
